descriptionHtml:
char is Ningheim Race with all the default body, brow, face, hair files that come with the mod

tatoo is from here http://www.nexusmods...im/mods/49853/?

freckle overlay from here http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/?

facial piercing is 'all piercings item' from mod http://www.nexusmods...im/mods/35056/?

you'll need chargen extension http://www.nexusmods...im/mods/36925/? and race menu http://www.nexusmods...im/mods/29624/?

after which, you should put the 0.slot in your datasksepluginchargenpresets folder

screenshots taken using the grim and somber enb http://www.nexusmods...im/mods/50501/? with the lut sepia optional pallete
author: naygor
